text: Liz Michelle de León Paz (born December 2, 1969 in Ciudad de Panamá, Panamá), is a Panamanian beauty winner of the Señorita Panamá 1990 title. Also represented Panama in Miss Universe 1991, the 40th Miss Universe pageant was held at Aladdin Theatre for the Performing Arts, Paradise, United States on May 17, 1991. De León, who is tall, competed in the national beauty pageant Señorita Panamá 1990, on August 10, 1990 and obtained the title of Señorita Panamá Universe. She represented Panamá Centro state. ==References== ==External links== * Señorita Panamá official website * Category:Living people Category:Miss Universe 1991 contestants Category:Panamanian beauty pageant winners Category:Señorita Panamá Category:1969 births
